description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be the shutdown of the Xbox 360 store after nearly 18 years of it's lifespan. With a bunch of games being lost in the process just how does one preserve this industry? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: The Xbox 360 WILL Die Tonight...
